<h2>Basic Hammock Care + Relaxation Tips</h2>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.2;">We like to call our hammocks "Backyard Heirlooms" -- with proper care + use, your Yellow Leaf Hammock or Hanging Chair will stay fresh + bright for years to come!</span></p>
<p>Your Yellow Leaf Hammock comes with a "hammock tote" for travel and storage, so make sure to keep the tote that your hammock arrives packaged in.</p>
<div class="offset-by-nine"></div>
<div class="offset-by-nine"> </div>
